<table class="table">
   <tr>
      <th>Date</th>
      <th>Assigned To</th>
      <th>Actual Approver</th>
      <th>Status</th>
      <th>Comments</th>
   </tr>
   <!--ko foreach: contextObject.approvalHistory--> <!-- ko foreach: steps --> 
   <tr>
      <td data-bind="dateText: theDate" /> 
      <td> <span data-bind="text: originalActor.name" /> </td>
      <td> <span data-bind="text: assignedActor.name" /> </td>
      <td data-bind="text: status" /> 
      <td data-bind="text: comments" /> 
   </tr>
   <!-- /ko --> <!-- /ko --> <script> function sortDates(a,b){if(a.theDate()<b.theDate()){return -1; }else if(Date.parse(a.theDate())> Date.parse(b.theDate())) {return 1; }else {return 0; } } </script> 
</table>
